      "comment": "MYSTERIOUS (2) turned in a plain performance last time when eighth at The Meadows over 525m behind Dustin (31.10) in a Mix 6/7 H. Has winning claims on her best figures. GO HOME GIRL (7) scored her maiden success two back then hit the frame last time when third and beaten one length at Sale over 435m (24.72). Will break from a wide draw. Rates a winning chance on best. PRICKLE (1) had been racing well with a Bottom Up - Grade 7 win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at this track. Can improve sharply here. CACKLING SUZIE (6) was well supported last time but could only manage second (25.41), beaten 0.8 lengths. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Well-placed to take this out.",
